      • addDevelopment

        public Development addDevelopment​(Development development)
        Appends the Development to the List of previous developments. If a Development mapped to the same User exists, nothing happens.
        Parameters:
        development - The Development to append.
        Returns:
        If successfully inserted, return the new Development, otherwise return the existing Development.
